WEBVTT

00:07.640 --> 00:08.920
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:37.040 --> 01:42.480
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:46.040 --> 01:51.840
THE GREAT BORDER GATE

01:55.400 --> 01:58.000
The… The Lord of Xiaonan rebelled.

02:02.000 --> 02:03.840
Return at once to tell Her Highness.

02:05.560 --> 02:07.520
Your Highness, Xiao Xun
killed the dispatch riders.

02:08.039 --> 02:09.520
We've lost contact with the Capital.

02:10.199 --> 02:12.720
All post houses along the way
are under his control.

02:13.320 --> 02:14.840
Rumors reached the Capital.

02:14.920 --> 02:15.800
Northern Desert Army
breached Bailang Pass.

02:16.680 --> 02:17.840
Yunzhong will fall in three days.

02:18.360 --> 02:20.600
They'll march for the imperial city.

02:22.680 --> 02:23.600
How's the Capital?

02:24.280 --> 02:25.720
Fifty thousand troops in the capital camp

02:25.800 --> 02:27.440
and one 100,000 nearby.
Why should we fear Xiao Xun?

02:28.120 --> 02:29.800
What we fear is that the commoners

02:29.880 --> 02:32.400
believe Xiao Xun's lie
to defend the Capital.

02:33.040 --> 02:34.120
In that case,

02:34.200 --> 02:36.320
he can rightfully
lead his troops into the city.

02:37.440 --> 02:39.000
If Xiao Xun enters the Capital,

02:39.800 --> 02:41.400
Yu's life will be in danger.

02:42.120 --> 02:43.520
Xie Yanfang is by Yu's side.

02:44.640 --> 02:45.560
He's ruthless.

02:46.840 --> 02:48.480
But his clan relies on Yu.

02:49.200 --> 02:50.600
Xie Yanfang will protect him.

02:52.280 --> 02:53.320
You're right.

02:54.000 --> 02:57.000
Xie Yanfang still has a crucial trick.

02:57.080 --> 02:58.400
This time,

02:59.360 --> 03:00.880
he'll definitely make this move.

03:02.400 --> 03:03.240
Get Xiaoman to me.

03:04.080 --> 03:04.920
Yes.

03:26.040 --> 03:27.400
CHU ZHAO

03:40.120 --> 03:42.760
Whatever you want me to do, let me know.

03:42.840 --> 03:45.440
All post houses along the way
have been cut off.

03:45.520 --> 03:47.320
I want you to take your men

03:47.400 --> 03:49.520
to bypass the post houses
and head for the Capital.

03:49.600 --> 03:52.680
Then, escort my cousin Chu Tang
and her family out of the Capital.

03:53.640 --> 03:54.920
Why all the trouble?

03:55.000 --> 03:57.760
Why don't we let her bring the news
of the frontier to the Capital?

03:57.840 --> 04:00.160
Who would believe a bandit?

04:01.520 --> 04:02.840
The public opinion in the Capital

04:02.920 --> 04:05.640
completely favors Xiao Xun,
who "guards" His Majesty.

04:08.000 --> 04:09.960
Then what is the problem
with Chu Tang's family?

04:10.560 --> 04:11.880
Chu Lan is a mere civil official.

04:11.960 --> 04:14.760
What danger justifies
all the effort to save him?

04:14.840 --> 04:15.960
In the Anping Rebellion,

04:16.040 --> 04:19.040
Xiao Xun used my uncle
to kill His Majesty.

04:19.120 --> 04:20.640
Now, he's the key witness.

04:20.720 --> 04:22.040
All parties will fight over him.

04:23.600 --> 04:24.440
I count on you.

04:25.240 --> 04:26.360
Don't worry. Leave it to me.

04:31.760 --> 04:33.960
What about you? To the Capital?

04:35.040 --> 04:35.960
No.

04:39.920 --> 04:41.760
I'm going somewhere else.

04:45.160 --> 04:47.000
TABLET OF LATE FATHER, CHU LING

04:47.080 --> 04:49.040
TABLET OF LATE MOTHER, MU MIANHONG

04:50.840 --> 04:51.920
Father.

04:52.920 --> 04:53.840
Mother.

04:55.040 --> 04:56.760
You were separated half your lives.

04:57.480 --> 05:01.720
Now you're finally reunited
in the underworld.

05:02.920 --> 05:03.920
Sadly,

05:06.080 --> 05:07.400
I have to leave.

05:08.720 --> 05:10.560
I'll keep defending the city

05:11.800 --> 05:13.040
Father left undefended.

05:15.120 --> 05:16.680
I'll continue the war

05:18.040 --> 05:19.200
Father left unfinished.

05:21.200 --> 05:24.000
Mother dreamed of peace
all over the world.

05:25.960 --> 05:27.520
I'll make it come true.

05:50.360 --> 05:52.640
THE CAPITAL

05:53.760 --> 05:56.560
I've heard Xiao Xun
has reached Baili Pavilion.

05:56.640 --> 05:59.360
A noble heir like him is always reliable.

05:59.440 --> 06:01.760
I believe soon, he'll rescue
the Capital from danger.

06:02.840 --> 06:04.400
He's been practicing martial arts
since childhood,

06:04.480 --> 06:05.880
and he leads elite troops.

06:05.960 --> 06:08.440
I hope he'll arrive soon.

06:09.200 --> 06:10.920
Since General Chu died,

06:11.000 --> 06:12.920
the Yunzhong troops
have been in utter chaos.

06:13.520 --> 06:15.720
They won't bother with the Capital.

06:15.800 --> 06:18.040
Luckily, His Highness is on his way here.

06:18.120 --> 06:19.720
Fair enough.

06:20.360 --> 06:24.000
The Grand Princess is brave,
but she's too young.

06:24.600 --> 06:26.440
We have to count on real royal members

06:27.040 --> 06:30.200
to guard the Capital
and protect our state.

06:32.480 --> 06:34.480
Jiang, the weather is lovely.

06:34.560 --> 06:36.200
Take Tang out for some fresh air.

06:36.880 --> 06:38.600
The tea has gone cold.

06:38.680 --> 06:39.760
The conversation is ironic.

06:40.360 --> 06:42.680
If she stays longer, she'll feel sick.

06:45.400 --> 06:46.920
Goodbye, then.

06:47.440 --> 06:48.280
Jiang.

06:49.680 --> 06:50.880
Why is she angry again?

06:55.440 --> 06:57.440
Mr. Xiao Xun is noble.

06:58.120 --> 07:00.960
Had General Chu not built
the city walls at great cost…

07:01.600 --> 07:02.920
Had Her Highness not guarded Wangcheng…

07:03.640 --> 07:04.840
You couldn't be sitting here,

07:05.480 --> 07:07.560
enjoying cold tea, or satirizing them.

07:08.640 --> 07:10.520
I advise you to hold your tongues.

07:18.200 --> 07:21.000
Jiang, I have a favor to ask.

07:21.600 --> 07:24.040
We're friends. Don't say that. What is it?

07:24.960 --> 07:26.600
I need help from your family.

07:30.040 --> 07:33.560
Mr. Xie, to what do I owe
the honor of this visit?

07:40.320 --> 07:42.240
I'm here to ask you, Mr. Deng.

07:43.800 --> 07:45.840
Do you really choose

07:47.720 --> 07:48.920
to throw your life away with Xiao Xun?

07:53.840 --> 07:55.160
What do you mean?

07:55.960 --> 07:58.160
I don't understand.

08:00.760 --> 08:02.800
Xiao Xun has reached Baili Pavilion.

08:02.880 --> 08:06.400
He keeps releasing messages
that he's coming to protect His Majesty.

08:07.120 --> 08:10.440
He expects a wide-open city gate
where people line up to welcome him.

08:10.520 --> 08:15.600
But do you know how we will end up

08:16.240 --> 08:17.840
if the city gate is open to him?

08:18.640 --> 08:20.160
Since it's the will of people,

08:20.680 --> 08:23.040
you should try to stop
the people in the Capital.

08:23.720 --> 08:27.320
What's the point of coming here
to stop me?

08:29.280 --> 08:30.720
Looks like you're determined

08:31.840 --> 08:33.200
to side with Mr. Xiao.

08:33.799 --> 08:35.760
They're within the defense line.

08:36.280 --> 08:37.799
The Capital is just ahead.

08:38.320 --> 08:40.400
If His Majesty still refuses
to open the gate,

08:41.120 --> 08:43.880
their advance will be an unauthorized move
and willful treason.

08:44.800 --> 08:46.400
After they enter the city,

08:46.480 --> 08:49.600
you might as well
find an excuse to kill them.

08:50.440 --> 08:52.600
You know people's will is irreversible.

08:53.320 --> 08:56.040
In their eyes, Xiao Xun

08:56.640 --> 08:59.040
is a meritorious protector
they're expecting.

09:00.120 --> 09:01.760
If His Majesty still refuses,

09:01.840 --> 09:03.800
people will complain.

09:03.880 --> 09:07.320
So, Mr. Xie, what do you intend to do?

09:12.760 --> 09:14.440
We must make Xiao Xun

09:15.160 --> 09:17.480
a rebel again.

09:17.560 --> 09:22.360
Are you saying
you'll prove his father's treason?

09:22.440 --> 09:23.360
Only in this way

09:23.960 --> 09:26.160
can we stop Xiao Xun from entering town.

09:26.240 --> 09:27.920
If he attacks by force,

09:28.000 --> 09:29.840
all the people will know

09:29.920 --> 09:32.440
that the court has no choice
but to fight back.

09:33.160 --> 09:38.240
If war breaks out,
the court will be rightful.

09:38.760 --> 09:40.840
We'll have no more worries,

09:40.920 --> 09:42.920
and all the people will submit.

09:43.960 --> 09:45.560
Then no one will question

09:47.320 --> 09:48.800
Yu's throne.

09:49.600 --> 09:52.520
Then how will you prove
the treason of the Lord of Xiaonan?

09:53.040 --> 09:54.280
Do you know

09:54.960 --> 10:00.960
Chu Lan was bribed by Xiao Xun
to poison Yu in Chu Mansion?

10:01.040 --> 10:02.760
You'll use Chu Lan as a scapegoat?

10:04.000 --> 10:05.080
Have you considered?

10:05.680 --> 10:09.080
If Chu Lan gets in trouble,
the Chu Family will be implicated.

10:09.680 --> 10:12.000
Then the Grand Princess
can hardly stay out of trouble.

10:13.040 --> 10:16.520
Great achievements
require great sacrifices.

10:17.640 --> 10:19.880
Only when we expose Xiao Xun's scheme

10:20.800 --> 10:22.120
can the two of us

10:23.280 --> 10:26.440
keep the city gate firmly shut.

10:27.200 --> 10:28.120
Isn't that so?

10:30.120 --> 10:31.880
I'm still curious about one thing.

10:33.080 --> 10:35.360
Xiao Xun wrote a letter to you.

10:35.880 --> 10:36.960
What was in…?

10:51.720 --> 10:55.000
After all that talking, I finally get it.

10:55.680 --> 10:57.200
You think Chu Lan isn't enough.

10:57.280 --> 10:59.360
You'll also get me involved

11:00.280 --> 11:02.240
to prove their treason.

11:03.880 --> 11:05.640
But have you thought about this?

11:05.720 --> 11:07.480
Is it a righteous war?

11:07.560 --> 11:09.320
Is it justified?

11:09.400 --> 11:11.240
You care. His Majesty cares.

11:12.800 --> 11:13.680
But I don't care.

11:16.080 --> 11:19.880
Don't try to keep your clan innocent
by ruining my reputation.

11:27.520 --> 11:28.640
You're wrong again.

11:30.240 --> 11:32.760
I just came here to give you a favor.

11:34.960 --> 11:36.680
Instead of keeping some secrets buried,

11:39.360 --> 11:41.520
why not turn them into your achievements?

11:53.040 --> 11:53.880
My Lord.

12:02.560 --> 12:05.040
Xie Yanfang wants to kill two birds
with one stone.

12:14.600 --> 12:16.560
TO OPEN THE GATE OR NOT

12:22.240 --> 12:25.160
Get ready. I'll see Chu Lan tonight.

12:25.920 --> 12:28.480
CHU MANSION

12:37.360 --> 12:39.880
My Lord, we looked everywhere.
No one is in.

12:42.080 --> 12:45.560
We asked the neighbors.
Nothing unusual was noticed.

12:45.640 --> 12:49.080
During the day, Chu Tang
even had tea with some ladies.

12:49.160 --> 12:51.240
As she came home,
she vanished into thin air.

12:51.920 --> 12:53.440
We may have early plans,

12:54.000 --> 12:55.800
but someone's always earlier.

12:55.880 --> 12:57.880
As soon as we had the idea,

12:58.680 --> 13:00.320
they had run away.

13:00.920 --> 13:02.240
How could they leave so perfectly?

13:02.320 --> 13:05.680
Theoretically, when Chu Zhao is away,

13:05.760 --> 13:08.880
Chu Lan should be isolated from the court.

13:09.640 --> 13:11.760
And Chu Lan doesn't look
like he can read the situation.

13:12.480 --> 13:16.000
Is it possible
that Her Highness sent them a message?

13:16.800 --> 13:18.600
Xiao Xun intercepted all the messages.

13:19.600 --> 13:21.640
How did Chu Zhao manage to send one?

13:28.760 --> 13:31.680
Xie Yanfang used up all his schemes.

13:31.760 --> 13:34.560
But his own ally stabbed him in the back.

13:36.520 --> 13:38.360
Send a message to Mr. Xie.

13:39.080 --> 13:41.480
Tell him the witness he longs for

13:44.280 --> 13:46.400
has fled.

13:46.480 --> 13:47.560
XIE RESIDENCE

13:47.640 --> 13:48.960
How come he fled?

13:49.480 --> 13:51.520
The Grand Princess

13:52.680 --> 13:55.640
has more political support
than I imagined.

13:55.720 --> 13:58.040
Of the clans that have ties
with the Chu Family,

13:58.120 --> 13:59.640
five left the city yesterday.

14:00.360 --> 14:02.760
Some said they went to rural houses.

14:02.840 --> 14:05.160
Some said they had an outing. And…

14:05.240 --> 14:07.520
Today, three ladies
met with Chu Tang in the day.

14:08.040 --> 14:09.320
Shall we pursue them?

14:13.120 --> 14:15.200
QI HONGYE EXCELS AT POLITICAL STRATEGY.
ZHOU MINGLI DEVOTES TO BE A SCHOLAR.

14:15.800 --> 14:17.400
It is time for us

14:19.680 --> 14:21.160
to go out and visit someone.

14:23.160 --> 14:26.160
ZHOU FAMILY’S FARMSTEAD

14:26.240 --> 14:32.480
‎ZHOU RESIDENCE

14:45.560 --> 14:46.480
Be careful, Mr. Chu.

14:46.560 --> 14:47.840
Come on, sweetheart.

14:51.520 --> 14:52.840
Hurry. Come, Tang.

14:59.600 --> 15:00.880
Jiang,

15:01.560 --> 15:03.480
-thank you.
-My pleasure.

15:04.320 --> 15:05.840
Don't thank me.

15:05.920 --> 15:08.680
Without my grandfather's approval,
I couldn't have helped you,

15:09.360 --> 15:10.320
even if I wanted to.

15:11.040 --> 15:12.800
Jiang, I need you

15:13.400 --> 15:14.720
to help my family leave.

15:14.800 --> 15:15.680
Why me?

15:15.760 --> 15:18.600
Shouldn't you beg some clan heads?

15:19.640 --> 15:21.120
I was told to ask them,

15:21.640 --> 15:23.000
but big clans have deep connections

15:23.080 --> 15:24.240
with shared interests.

15:25.000 --> 15:25.840
I…

15:26.920 --> 15:27.760
I thought about it.

15:28.640 --> 15:29.480
You're the only one

15:30.080 --> 15:31.520
I can entrust my life to.

15:32.960 --> 15:34.040
At the Hai hour tonight,

15:34.120 --> 15:37.000
my carriage will pick you up
at the back door of Chu Mansion.

15:38.000 --> 15:39.120
I shall remember

15:40.680 --> 15:42.760
your great favor.

15:44.760 --> 15:45.800
Go get some rest.

16:00.680 --> 16:01.920
Come on, Tang.

16:02.000 --> 16:04.120
Your uncle and his daughter
are so useless.

16:04.200 --> 16:06.840
We shouldn't have
expected them to bring glory.

16:07.920 --> 16:08.840
You…

16:10.440 --> 16:14.360
Luckily, our daughter is farsighted
and gets along with other noble ladies.

16:15.440 --> 16:17.480
Madam, you sound so proud.

16:18.600 --> 16:19.640
Do you really think

16:19.720 --> 16:22.600
her mere friendship
can get you through the city defense?

16:23.480 --> 16:25.440
The Grand Princess
arranged deceptive schemes

16:25.520 --> 16:27.480
and sent bandits to clear enemy sentries.

16:28.200 --> 16:30.840
Otherwise, you wouldn't
have come here alive.

16:30.920 --> 16:33.360
-You… You are…
-Yes.

16:33.960 --> 16:37.240
We're the bandits
whom people like you despise most.

16:42.760 --> 16:44.320
Her Highness sent me to get you.
Don't yell.

16:45.080 --> 16:46.520
Nod, and I'll let you go.

16:57.440 --> 17:01.120
<i>The Lord of Xiaonan isn't a defender,</i>
<i>but a usurper.</i>

17:01.760 --> 17:03.720
<i>To reveal Xiao Xun's true colors,</i>

17:03.800 --> 17:05.319
<i>the court will dig up the evidence</i>

17:05.400 --> 17:07.480
<i>your father nearly killed</i>
<i>the young emperor.</i>

17:08.119 --> 17:09.040
<i>Danger.</i>

17:10.920 --> 17:13.640
Her Highness said the heads
of these clans are reliable.

17:13.720 --> 17:14.560
Go ask them for help.

17:18.560 --> 17:20.280
CHU ZHAO

17:20.359 --> 17:22.839
-Darling.
-Xiaoman, let's leave.

17:23.359 --> 17:24.720
This is a bestowal to Jiang's ancestors.

17:25.400 --> 17:26.680
It must be on record
with the Ministry of War.

17:27.680 --> 17:28.520
Within half a day,

17:29.120 --> 17:30.560
we will all get caught.

17:31.560 --> 17:34.920
Tang, how could you
still doubt the Zhou Family?

17:35.000 --> 17:37.840
Just now, Miss Zhou seemed
she truly wanted to help us.

17:37.920 --> 17:41.160
Father, Jiang truly wants to help us.

17:41.680 --> 17:44.280
That's why we can't get her involved.

17:44.360 --> 17:45.920
-But they--
-Stop lingering.

17:46.000 --> 17:46.880
Go with me.

17:48.160 --> 17:49.760
-Let's go. Hurry.
-But they…

17:49.840 --> 17:50.680
Oh, darling.

18:21.800 --> 18:23.800
‎ZHOU BING, MINISTER OF CEREMONIES OF CHU

18:25.040 --> 18:27.520
My Lord, Chu Lan's trail is gone.

18:40.480 --> 18:43.280
Mr. Zhou, you really made
very cunning moves.

18:48.960 --> 18:49.880
No offense,

18:52.400 --> 18:54.280
but I gave up a piece to get ahead.

18:59.480 --> 19:00.320
Mr. Xie,

19:00.400 --> 19:03.640
you're still so enigmatic
when playing Liubo.

19:07.160 --> 19:12.960
I wonder what you're fighting for
in this round.

19:18.040 --> 19:19.800
When the Lord of Xuan played with me,

19:20.960 --> 19:23.400
he wrongfully killed
a loyal man over one piece.

19:24.240 --> 19:25.240
In today's game,

19:26.400 --> 19:28.400
I'm fighting for His Majesty's life.

19:38.560 --> 19:39.800
The Lord of Xiaonan and his heir

19:39.880 --> 19:42.200
nearly took His Majesty's life.

19:43.200 --> 19:44.640
Chu Lan is the witness.

19:45.240 --> 19:50.200
So, I hope you will help His Majesty
to reveal the truth to people.

20:04.760 --> 20:08.160
Over generations, my clan
has been a bystander.

20:08.240 --> 20:11.440
Mr. Xie, you don't need
to probe me like this.

20:12.320 --> 20:16.240
I don't know where Chu Lan is.

20:22.000 --> 20:22.960
Mr. Zhou,

20:24.280 --> 20:26.320
you must know no one can be

20:27.440 --> 20:30.000
a bystander in chaotic times.

20:31.960 --> 20:33.920
My Lord, we've searched. Nothing.

20:35.520 --> 20:36.360
Yes.

20:40.160 --> 20:41.240
Sorry for the offense.

20:41.920 --> 20:43.320
I'll take my leave.

20:45.480 --> 20:46.360
Oh.

20:48.000 --> 20:49.320
It's too windy tonight.

20:50.560 --> 20:52.280
Remember to close your windows.

20:55.640 --> 20:58.360
Mr. Xie, please see yourself out.

21:01.240 --> 21:02.920
My Lady, be careful.

21:05.960 --> 21:07.240
Father.

21:07.320 --> 21:10.120
The carriage that took them
out of town is back.

21:10.200 --> 21:11.480
Shall we make early preparations?

21:11.560 --> 21:14.480
If Mr. Xie really
finds out something, then…

21:14.560 --> 21:17.400
Jiang did something reckless.

21:17.480 --> 21:20.840
But since we promised to help,
we won't complain.

21:26.600 --> 21:30.680
Between the Grand Princess
and Mr. Xie, there will be

21:33.120 --> 21:35.280
a long game of strategy.

21:35.360 --> 21:37.480
XIE RESIDENCE

21:37.560 --> 21:39.520
Welcome, Mr. Deng.

21:39.600 --> 21:41.280
We are honored by your presence.

21:48.880 --> 21:50.440
This orchid is very delicate.

21:51.560 --> 21:53.000
No strangers shall touch it.

21:53.600 --> 21:55.440
You tend this flower so well.

21:56.040 --> 21:59.000
Sadly, its roots have rotted.

21:59.960 --> 22:01.640
It barely appears to bloom.

22:03.120 --> 22:04.640
You've searched the whole day.

22:05.480 --> 22:06.720
Have you found what you're after?

22:12.880 --> 22:15.160
The Grand Princess is so far away,

22:15.680 --> 22:18.080
but big clans give her generous support.

22:18.960 --> 22:21.160
She does have great influence.

22:22.000 --> 22:25.560
You didn't come here
just to satirize me, did you?

22:26.480 --> 22:28.640
Do you know where Chu Zhao is?

22:29.680 --> 22:32.480
She's riding at full speed toward Xiaonan.

22:32.560 --> 22:36.560
Does she think Xiao Xun
will retreat when his father is trapped?

22:38.680 --> 22:39.840
How childish.

22:40.440 --> 22:42.800
Her Highness will suppress the rebels
on His Majesty's behalf.

22:43.640 --> 22:44.600
What's wrong with it?

22:45.760 --> 22:47.480
Her Highness has great influence.

22:47.560 --> 22:50.720
Since she dares,
she must be confident enough.

22:51.320 --> 22:52.240
Yeah.

22:52.920 --> 22:55.080
You and Her Highness
used to have the same goal.

22:55.160 --> 22:57.000
You were both against Xiao Xun.

22:57.600 --> 23:00.720
But you insist on using
Chu Lan as a scapegoat

23:00.800 --> 23:03.200
and getting her clan involved.

23:04.240 --> 23:05.200
Obviously,

23:06.360 --> 23:08.160
Chu Zhao wouldn't agree.

23:08.240 --> 23:10.200
That's a bit much, Mr. Deng.

23:11.720 --> 23:13.560
As long as you approve the edict

23:13.640 --> 23:17.840
that Xiao Xun instigated Chu Lan
to poison the imperial grandson,

23:18.640 --> 23:21.040
Her Highness will be
suppressing the rebels

23:21.120 --> 23:22.320
with a valid reason.

23:23.000 --> 23:25.960
I'm helping her, aren't I?

23:29.000 --> 23:31.200
Have you heard about this?

23:31.280 --> 23:35.000
An orchid dies,
but its fragrance will linger.

23:35.080 --> 23:36.640
Someone

23:38.160 --> 23:40.120
only gets in the way when he's alive.

23:41.560 --> 23:43.440
Mr. Xie, you have

23:43.520 --> 23:45.200
a very clever plan.

23:47.360 --> 23:48.640
I'll take my leave.

23:52.680 --> 23:53.800
Mr. Deng.

23:55.920 --> 23:57.480
We're just serving the state

23:58.000 --> 23:59.720
by cutting out the deadwood.

24:12.240 --> 24:13.320
‎EDICT TO DEPOSE THE RENEGADE OFFICIAL

24:13.400 --> 24:14.360
What's this?

24:14.440 --> 24:16.160
Why is Zhao guilty?

24:18.360 --> 24:19.240
Don't, Your Majesty.

24:32.080 --> 24:32.920
Your Majesty,

24:34.120 --> 24:35.120
this edict says

24:35.200 --> 24:38.480
her uncle Chu Lan is guilty.
Did you forget?

24:39.160 --> 24:40.760
He tried to poison you back then.

24:40.840 --> 24:43.640
So, Her Highness
took you away from her family.

24:44.160 --> 24:45.760
So, Chu Lan is really guilty.

24:47.560 --> 24:49.360
Then why did no one tell me about it?

24:50.120 --> 24:52.160
Chu Lan is Zhao's uncle.

24:52.240 --> 24:55.240
If he's guilty, she will be implicated.

24:56.080 --> 24:57.760
Now, the situation is complicated.

24:58.600 --> 25:00.760
Lord of Xiaonan and his heir
intend rebellion.

25:00.840 --> 25:03.000
Xiao Xun is coming as a defender.

25:03.520 --> 25:05.000
Our people support him.

25:05.520 --> 25:07.400
Ministers want the city gate
to be opened too.

25:08.160 --> 25:10.280
But if he leads
his 100,000 troops into town

25:10.360 --> 25:12.440
without firing a single shot,

25:13.360 --> 25:14.520
we won't be able to resist.

25:15.120 --> 25:16.600
The casualties will be terrible.

25:18.160 --> 25:19.680
What we should do now

25:20.200 --> 25:24.160
is let the entire world know
the sins of Xiao Xun and his father.

25:24.920 --> 25:26.320
Then we'll all rise against them.

25:29.440 --> 25:30.760
You're bullying Zhao.

25:31.360 --> 25:34.600
You're bullying her
just because her father is gone.

25:38.840 --> 25:39.840
Yu,

25:42.080 --> 25:44.040
no one is bullying your sister.

25:44.640 --> 25:46.000
If she were here now,

25:47.280 --> 25:48.640
she would do the same.

25:53.560 --> 25:55.800
The post houses have been cut off.

25:55.880 --> 25:57.880
But the men I sent out learnt something.

25:57.960 --> 26:00.640
Xiao Xun intercepted a victory report.

26:00.720 --> 26:02.280
Not long ago,

26:02.360 --> 26:05.400
Chu Zhao led a raid
against Northern Desert Royal Army,

26:05.480 --> 26:06.760
driving them back a hundred li.

26:08.520 --> 26:09.400
And later,

26:10.160 --> 26:12.200
the enemy relaunched an attack.

26:12.280 --> 26:15.200
Once again, she led troops to crush them.

26:16.120 --> 26:17.160
She did?

26:18.760 --> 26:19.600
What's more,

26:20.120 --> 26:22.920
on hearing Xiao Xun was leading troops
to surround the Capital,

26:23.000 --> 26:25.840
she led forces to attack Xiaonan.

26:26.400 --> 26:27.440
Do you know why?

26:28.640 --> 26:30.360
"Besiege Wei to rescue Zhao."
I've read about that.

26:32.080 --> 26:33.040
That's right.

26:34.320 --> 26:35.560
So you don't need to worry.

26:36.240 --> 26:38.480
Your sister fears nothing.

26:39.080 --> 26:40.600
No one can bully her easily.

26:41.280 --> 26:43.560
She's defending our state and our people.

26:44.200 --> 26:47.760
Even when her uncle is guilty,
she won't be implicated.

26:49.400 --> 26:50.480
Do you trust me?

26:51.760 --> 26:52.600
I trust you.

27:05.600 --> 27:07.760
CHU LAN PLOTTED REGICIDE WITH XIAO XUN.
TITLES REVOKED. ASSETS SEIZED. IMPRISONED.

27:17.400 --> 27:20.360
XIAONAN PREFECTURE

27:26.080 --> 27:26.920
I never thought

27:28.360 --> 27:31.720
I could have a battle
against the Grand Princess.

27:32.240 --> 27:35.360
How dare she besiege us
with only a few thousand troops?

27:35.960 --> 27:37.320
A warrior's daughter?

27:37.400 --> 27:40.960
I think the great reputation of Chu Ling

27:41.040 --> 27:44.680
will just be ruined by his daughter
who has a swollen head.

27:45.520 --> 27:47.320
Your Lordship, don't bother with her.

27:47.400 --> 27:48.880
I'll go teach her a lesson.

27:51.200 --> 27:53.600
Your Lordship, the Grand Princess
wants to talk.

27:53.680 --> 27:55.800
The Grand Princess? What's she doing here?

27:57.400 --> 27:58.920
Since she wants to talk,

27:59.440 --> 28:02.720
tell her I have trouble walking
and can't go out.

28:03.480 --> 28:06.720
However, my gate is always open to her.

28:07.440 --> 28:09.080
She can come anytime.

28:09.600 --> 28:11.400
XIAONAN

28:11.480 --> 28:13.480
We both know it's an ambush.

28:14.480 --> 28:15.880
If you enter his mansion,

28:15.960 --> 28:17.040
you'll be walking
straight into the lion's den.

28:17.800 --> 28:20.120
If Xiaonan holds you as a hostage,

28:20.720 --> 28:22.160
the Capital will face a tough choice.

28:22.680 --> 28:23.520
You worry too much.

28:24.240 --> 28:27.320
Mr. Deng and Xie Yanfang
can't wait for me to die for the state.

28:28.160 --> 28:31.400
Believe it or not,
they've even prepared my posthumous title.

28:32.200 --> 28:33.480
This is no child's play.

28:34.240 --> 28:35.240
Are you really sure?

28:35.760 --> 28:36.880
I know what worries you.

28:36.960 --> 28:39.240
The Lord of Xiaonan is so cunning

28:39.320 --> 28:41.640
that he even rebels
in the name of guarding His Majesty.

28:42.880 --> 28:45.160
If the Grand Princess dies in his mansion,

28:45.760 --> 28:47.560
guess how history will judge him.

28:48.200 --> 28:51.480
He will be a traitor,
whether he likes it or not.

28:52.160 --> 28:53.040
So…

28:56.200 --> 28:59.120
Will you take this gamble with me?

29:01.280 --> 29:02.120
Of course.

29:02.200 --> 29:03.960
Not to mention his mansion,

29:04.040 --> 29:06.280
I'll even follow you

29:07.160 --> 29:08.000
to the underworld.

29:12.560 --> 29:13.400
This time,

29:15.880 --> 29:17.120
we'll all live well.

29:20.920 --> 29:22.120
We must live.

30:03.160 --> 30:06.040
XIAONAN

30:09.000 --> 30:10.520
What an impressive mansion.

30:11.120 --> 30:12.240
Look at the scale.

30:12.320 --> 30:15.880
He's so obviously showing
his ambition to be the Emperor.

30:17.080 --> 30:20.680
Then, I'll kill that hope of his.

30:47.360 --> 30:48.840
<i>WEILIAOZI: ON MILITARY STRATEGY</i>

31:15.760 --> 31:17.960
How could we reject the tea he offered?

31:19.760 --> 31:21.880
You've got some spine, Miss Chu.

31:23.240 --> 31:26.440
Don't you fear I may put something
in the tea?

31:26.960 --> 31:29.840
I am the Grand Princess of State.

31:31.240 --> 31:33.920
I can fight battles with you
and slaughter your men.

31:35.360 --> 31:37.440
If I were to die from poisoned tea,

31:37.960 --> 31:40.800
people in the world would laugh at you.

31:45.440 --> 31:47.040
Even if I were bloodthirsty,

31:47.120 --> 31:49.240
I would know I should keep
worthy generals alive.

31:50.200 --> 31:52.920
Besides, I've admired General Chu.

31:53.560 --> 31:54.760
He's gone.

31:54.840 --> 31:57.800
I still count on you
to inherit his legacy.

31:58.320 --> 31:59.560
How would I try to kill you?

32:00.160 --> 32:01.440
You flatter me.

32:03.600 --> 32:04.680
In that case,

32:05.200 --> 32:08.000
please withdraw your troops
that are besieging the Capital.

32:09.880 --> 32:13.240
Don't let common folks die
in your fight for the throne.

32:14.640 --> 32:16.520
As a general's daughter,

32:17.360 --> 32:19.400
you must be familiar
with military classics.

32:22.240 --> 32:25.400
Have you read about this?
Glory for one, death for thousands.

32:26.600 --> 32:28.600
New dynasty rises, the old one falls.

32:28.680 --> 32:32.520
Someone must sweep away the incense ash

32:33.040 --> 32:34.520
before burning new incense.

32:35.120 --> 32:38.440
If His Majesty grants you the Golden Seal

32:39.320 --> 32:40.920
and feudal sovereignty,

32:42.240 --> 32:43.400
will you stop the war?

32:44.880 --> 32:48.800
Your Highness, when His Lordship
can get the Imperial Seal,

32:48.880 --> 32:50.880
why would he need the Golden Seal?

32:53.480 --> 32:56.760
You offered a great deal
to make me retreat.

32:57.360 --> 33:01.400
But how dare a woman like you
grant me feudal sovereignty?

33:02.640 --> 33:04.920
When I grant something, you will get it.

33:13.520 --> 33:15.280
Now, I understand.

33:15.360 --> 33:17.320
You aren't persuading me

33:17.400 --> 33:20.800
for the young emperor
or the ministers in the court.

33:22.000 --> 33:25.240
You're trying to stop me
for the sake of the people.

33:27.680 --> 33:29.520
What a saint you are.

33:31.240 --> 33:32.800
I'm not a saint.

33:35.240 --> 33:37.920
I am the Grand Princess of State.

33:38.520 --> 33:40.560
I won't see this state fall apart.

33:41.880 --> 33:43.400
Like I said,

33:43.480 --> 33:46.520
I've admired General Chu,
and I think highly of you.

33:47.920 --> 33:48.880
What about

33:50.440 --> 33:53.040
you and I working together?

33:58.520 --> 33:59.360
How?

34:00.840 --> 34:04.160
If I become the Emperor,
Xun will be the Crown Prince,

34:04.240 --> 34:05.640
and you'll be the Crown Princess.

34:06.240 --> 34:07.960
Then you'll be the Empress.

34:09.080 --> 34:10.159
I can also grant you

34:10.239 --> 34:14.360
the command over frontier troops,
unrestrained by the court's Tally.

34:15.639 --> 34:16.560
Do you agree?

34:22.480 --> 34:24.520
So, being Xiao Xun's empress

34:25.560 --> 34:27.320
can get me such great power.

34:27.400 --> 34:29.159
I'm not kidding.

34:29.880 --> 34:30.880
I know.

34:32.080 --> 34:34.320
You really mean it.

34:35.199 --> 34:36.199
Too bad, though.

34:37.239 --> 34:38.639
Am I offering not enough?

34:38.719 --> 34:41.080
Feel free to make any other requests.

34:41.880 --> 34:43.639
I have only one request.

34:44.400 --> 34:46.840
I request you to stop the war.

34:51.520 --> 34:53.480
You need to understand one thing.

34:54.600 --> 34:56.440
I can persuade you.

34:56.520 --> 34:58.720
You're in no position to persuade me.

34:59.560 --> 35:01.400
I'm not here to persuade you,

35:02.280 --> 35:03.680
but threaten you.

35:06.800 --> 35:08.840
With what can you threaten me?

35:11.080 --> 35:12.000
Xiao Xun.

35:25.280 --> 35:27.000
Speaking of him,

35:27.600 --> 35:30.160
he has still kept your birthdate card.

35:30.920 --> 35:34.680
He knelt for three days and nights,
swearing to marry no one but you.

35:35.280 --> 35:37.680
But you requested
to annul your engagement.

35:38.440 --> 35:42.400
Xun still hasn't figured out
what he did wrong.

35:43.560 --> 35:44.760
Today,

35:45.720 --> 35:47.800
I know the answer.

35:52.920 --> 35:55.000
You must be Commander Xie.

35:56.800 --> 35:58.920
I've heard a lot about you.

35:59.000 --> 36:00.840
You're as remarkable as people say.

36:02.160 --> 36:03.320
During the coup,

36:03.400 --> 36:06.320
you led a few guards
to defeat ten thousand troops.

36:06.400 --> 36:07.600
You are a real hero.

36:09.680 --> 36:12.120
Your Lordship, don't be ridiculous.

36:12.640 --> 36:16.480
I broke off my engagement
for the people of our state,

36:17.000 --> 36:18.920
not for romance.

36:20.720 --> 36:22.720
Narrow-minded as you are,

36:23.240 --> 36:24.520
how can you fight for the throne?

36:26.200 --> 36:27.760
What a sharp tongue.

36:28.760 --> 36:30.760
If I remember correctly, Mr. Xie,

36:31.280 --> 36:34.840
your brother also has great ambitions.

36:35.480 --> 36:38.880
If one day you meet in armed conflict,
whose side will you take?

36:42.160 --> 36:45.000
I pledge loyalty to His Majesty,
the Grand Princess,

36:45.800 --> 36:47.240
and the State of Chu.

36:47.760 --> 36:51.280
Anyone who hurts the imperial heir
or the Grand Princess

37:01.680 --> 37:03.480
will be my enemy.

37:04.200 --> 37:06.600
You're truly a hero
who is worth a hundred men.

37:08.120 --> 37:09.600
Remarkable, indeed.

37:11.880 --> 37:15.960
Do you know he isn't the only one
who is worth a hundred?

37:17.480 --> 37:18.600
There's also the Longwei Army.

37:21.080 --> 37:22.360
The Longwei Army?

37:22.440 --> 37:24.800
You must've heard about the Longwei Army.

37:25.440 --> 37:28.720
They put down the rebellion
while outnumbered.

37:29.360 --> 37:31.560
My father devotedly trained them.

37:31.640 --> 37:35.720
They move like ghosts
and scatter around in disguise.

37:36.520 --> 37:39.800
How can you be sure
there aren't any in your mansion?

37:45.400 --> 37:47.400
If you agree to retreat,

37:48.800 --> 37:49.920
I'll pretend nothing happened.

37:50.800 --> 37:52.760
So, this is how you threaten me.

37:54.040 --> 37:58.920
You want to use the Longwei Army
to kill my son as well as me.

37:59.000 --> 38:02.040
You can take this as a gamble.

38:02.960 --> 38:04.320
Five thousand soldiers outside the town.

38:05.000 --> 38:06.920
Five thousand of the Longwei Army in town.

38:07.440 --> 38:10.680
If they join hands,

38:11.960 --> 38:13.480
how will you handle it?

38:19.520 --> 38:20.520
Someone.

38:21.040 --> 38:24.000
Get the rooms ready.
Give Her Highness a warm reception.

38:31.480 --> 38:32.920
The secret guards in this room
can be withdrawn.

38:35.120 --> 38:37.960
With poor inner power and uneven breath,

38:39.320 --> 38:40.240
they're useless.

38:46.120 --> 38:49.640
Your Lordship, Xie Yanlai
is no ordinary man.

38:49.720 --> 38:52.240
When he's around Chu Zhao,
we can hardly hurt her.

38:53.440 --> 38:55.480
Ning Kun, you have no idea.

38:56.280 --> 38:58.600
Chu Ling and the late emperor
trained the Longwei Army.

38:59.600 --> 39:02.320
The scariest thing about them is,

39:02.400 --> 39:04.400
we don't know who they are,

39:04.480 --> 39:06.800
and we don't know
when or where they'll appear.

39:08.120 --> 39:09.880
They're unpreventable.

39:10.640 --> 39:12.600
Tell Xun to be on guard.

39:13.120 --> 39:14.040
Yes.

39:19.480 --> 39:20.480
In such a big courtyard,

39:21.280 --> 39:22.760
I can't even hear a bird.

39:23.600 --> 39:24.960
It's eerily quiet.

39:30.160 --> 39:31.000
Careful.

39:34.120 --> 39:36.040
Lord of Xiaonan has great taste.

39:36.120 --> 39:39.800
He even uses the best tea
for mere visitors.

39:40.400 --> 39:42.600
Too bad, though. The tea got cold.

39:42.680 --> 39:44.160
We know it's an ambush,

39:44.840 --> 39:46.400
and we should be more cautious.

39:46.480 --> 39:47.840
What if he poisoned the tea?

39:47.920 --> 39:48.960
He wouldn't dare.

39:50.200 --> 39:51.400
Not now, at least.

39:52.000 --> 39:54.120
What he wants is to be legitimate.

39:54.840 --> 39:57.920
If I die in his place, have a guess.

39:58.440 --> 40:00.920
Will people spit and drown this place?

40:07.680 --> 40:11.400
You know the Longwei Army
isn't in Xiaonan,

40:11.480 --> 40:13.480
but you bluffed just like that.

40:14.800 --> 40:16.560
Didn't you fear that he could
see through you?

40:17.200 --> 40:18.360
Let me tell you this.

40:18.440 --> 40:20.200
What makes the Longwei Army terrifying

40:20.280 --> 40:22.880
is that people believe they're everywhere.

40:30.640 --> 40:31.800
Don't worry.

40:32.360 --> 40:34.920
Someone's having a harder time.

40:35.440 --> 40:36.800
His Lordship is cautious by nature.

40:36.880 --> 40:39.960
Without a perfect plan,
he wouldn't act rashly.

40:40.040 --> 40:43.720
He sent Xiao Xun to the Capital
because he thought the time was right.

40:45.120 --> 40:46.880
The calmer we are,

40:47.480 --> 40:50.640
the more he will doubt his own judgment.

40:51.360 --> 40:53.240
When he thinks it's not the right time,

40:54.640 --> 40:56.000
he'll ask Xiao Xun to retreat.

40:56.600 --> 40:58.520
So, just now, you were trying

40:59.640 --> 41:00.840
to break his will,

41:01.760 --> 41:04.120
making him think his plan wasn't perfect.

41:04.200 --> 41:06.160
Then he'll lose his cool

41:06.240 --> 41:07.760
-and withdraw.
-That's right.

41:07.840 --> 41:11.800
So, Jiu, don't be impatient.
We'll just wait.

41:12.960 --> 41:14.360
We'll wait patiently

41:15.600 --> 41:16.920
until he makes his decision.

41:17.960 --> 41:21.200
I've heard this is the best scenic spot
all over this mansion.

41:22.720 --> 41:25.640
Let's not waste his hospitality.
